{"tid":1634860,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完winter on fire有感而發 大人真係垃圾","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T15:29:45.000Z","uid":9499,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c832d2a4ddb005b7652ed9dfa22fa5d9b94a39","tid":1634860,"uid":9499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"套docu的確有好多值得參考嘅嘢<br />\n例如人民反抗嘅心、即時戰略、救手足嘅意志<br />\n<br />\n但最想講嘅係點解啲大人只依賴細路 從來唔提供物資，甚至好多有車嘅都只用嚟義載？<br />\n明明可以提供好多武器防具俾前線<br />\n車又可以用嚟載物資同工具、載食物<br />\n點解每次開花都只係得啲戴住豬咀嘅後生上前？班大人就喺後面食花生乜撚都唔做<br />\n把口講幾撐我地，但出親嚟就乜撚都唔做，甚至匿喺屋企<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚心淡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UxV5pqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxV5pqs.jpg&h=afd4620e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12b81604c1e525dfdce1c4e2920edffbbea50854","tid":1634860,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:29:15.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文見此：<br />\n<br />\n【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家一定要繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"406c972746987f56b90d71e92b8e5ce387f966b3","tid":1634860,"uid":126062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日十月八 全民三罷 全港繼續死城 </span></span></strong><br />\n有冇人跟！！有既急需文宣！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634432/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634432/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8f65191d995eb9b79fa181648569ae755445955e","tid":1634860,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 連登開左英文台！English Channel is LIVE now on LIHKG!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634824</a>"},{"pid":"adc65186c4140d4be2d3b08ef14b54f2f7628364","tid":1634860,"uid":9499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bc5776b3b12d73f297e56077aaa0dd1618a418d","tid":1634860,"uid":146184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"啲大人唔會想聽真話，要自己呃自己呀，你唔好拆穿晒佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfd9184c9be0fc07343fce347930970550c7fe6","tid":1634860,"uid":35262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:09:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48e9f22075fa36e41be9a834e81b1275afc7a31b","tid":1634860,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=147dc194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"72db0d38117cb5736b1d171403e3c0448d366e64","tid":1634860,"uid":228049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"只可以話你口中好嘅大人唔係冇，只不過唔多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb44957732ea9fddb7115bf27cf86c23557dd93","tid":1634860,"uid":264956,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"72db0d38117cb5736b1d171403e3c0448d366e64","tid":1634860,"uid":228049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"只可以話你口中好嘅大人唔係冇，只不過唔多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:36:21.000Z","msg":"其實好多人出黎行及課金都叫出分力，唔通養緊細路個d一家大細要走上前線，只可以講每人只能按自己可承擔既付出，大人都明白後生為自己爭取y<br />\n站在背後，亦有唔少都站在前線，被捕者都有大人，你要講就話個d只要求飼料既大人喇。"},{"pid":"4568f6ad662ef6b5b96f1b3649e3d25c052caada","tid":1634860,"uid":9499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:33:14.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796815beffcead7816f7d66083ce78362b03bbcb","tid":1634860,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"純化左<br />\n比上一代社會規則限死左自己思維<br />\n同時間因為有埋家庭呢個因素而唔想突破犯法呢條線<br />\n所以可以理解點解佢地最盡都係課金同義載"},{"pid":"12bdf71715f51fd827d5c555be19e2e1bb77dcc8","tid":1634860,"uid":59868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"講左好耐係要武器<br />\n而家甚至連豬嘴都唔再需要<br />\n因為無反抗手段既話<br />\n你連留守既機會都無<br />\n有車既我都唔知點解唔幫手車武器<br />\n講到而家都重未做到人人魔法<br />\n咁學咩人講反抗"},{"pid":"9b0e7658dfc8258d27e81d043f6cc67535cf7cad","tid":1634860,"uid":286206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"好多後生都話大人垃圾<br />\n之後時日過去，自己就會變成當年口中既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大越大越無成本去做你地做既野，佢地要顧屋企顧呢樣顧果樣<br />\n你可以唔認同，但呢個事實。時間耐了你有一日會明白。佢地背後有出錢同義載已經算好。河況其實好多人放左工都出去發夢。唔好過份Idealize呢個世界。"},{"pid":"52dd324679db30d9cf84541b93109ef61f49fac4","tid":1634860,"uid":236348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:08:39.000Z","msg":"呢樣嘢冇係香港發生。林鄭都有講，被捕人士約28%是學生，至最近升至43%，你口中嘅大人都佔被捕者大多數。<br />\n<br />\n但香港的確有班藍屍廢老，冇幫手不特止，仲不停抹黑示威者，呢班先真係仆街。<br />\n<br />\n最後，勿分化，我呢次當你無心，下次實屌爆你。"},{"pid":"e037f72df3fe16fa0b293a2398da64a14240e903","tid":1634860,"uid":9499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12bdf71715f51fd827d5c555be19e2e1bb77dcc8","tid":1634860,"uid":59868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"講左好耐係要武器<br />\n而家甚至連豬嘴都唔再需要<br />\n因為無反抗手段既話<br />\n你連留守既機會都無<br />\n有車既我都唔知點解唔幫手車武器<br />\n講到而家都重未做到人人魔法<br />\n咁學咩人講反抗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"好認同<br />\n齋滅火嚟cover手足根本做唔到咩嘢<br />\n得一兩個有棍<br />\n大佬 俾啲雷球棍同埋高爾夫球棍都好呀<br />\n個個都得豬咀同埋盾 齋防守唔進攻嘅仗係贏唔到"},{"pid":"5be0b8e42ae094a02c2f8e3d937ac9af4cc82408","tid":1634860,"uid":9499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52dd324679db30d9cf84541b93109ef61f49fac4","tid":1634860,"uid":236348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:08:39.000Z","msg":"呢樣嘢冇係香港發生。林鄭都有講，被捕人士約28%是學生，至最近升至43%，你口中嘅大人都佔被捕者大多數。<br />\n<br />\n但香港的確有班藍屍廢老，冇幫手不特止，仲不停抹黑示威者，呢班先真係仆街。<br />\n<br />\n最後，勿分化，我呢次當你無心，下次實屌爆你。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"唔好意思手足，我原意唔係分化 可能我講得唔好<br />\n只係想屌柒啲得把口但明明有資源可以提供嘅大人<br />\n我明白被捕當中都有大人 亦都好多謝佢地對呢場仗嘅付出<br />\n我焦點係放喺提供資源方面 明明有能力可以做更多又唔洗拋頭露面怕被捕 但都係唔去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我永不分化 不割蓆 但指責只想令大家進步<br />\n第一次開post，有講得唔好嘅地方請見諒"},{"pid":"0b50bb896e55f39464a78762b666e04334acdfa8","tid":1634860,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"到你大左都係咁<br />\n我睇撚死你丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb093ad2f90f7fc305b8e8926a83ea79bff4493","tid":1634860,"uid":236348,"like